      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an impeccable 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This S54-powered icon features a high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this chassis has been fastidiously maintained with a reinforced rear subframe, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and a recent rod bearing service for total peace of mind. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers to retain its legendary handling characteristics. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. This is a turn-key, investment-quality example for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
